{"tid":2234382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟張敬軒有幾自大：【自泰國捐精後】軒仔盤點撞樣藝人：周街都見到自己","createTime":"2020-10-08T00:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T14:15:31.000Z","uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf73f0419cb41f960f98121998cc98e1820877b6","tid":2234382,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"講真我覺得好多個都唔似囉　求其擺個POSE一樣就係似咩<br />\n成日講到自己好靚又正<br />\n咪又係護旗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手張敬軒日前玩變臉App，「變肥」後竟然同肥媽撞樣，隨即引起熱議。其實張敬軒以往都曾與唔少人撞樣，呢日佢就喺社交網盤點同佢似樣嘅藝人名人，當中包括倪晨曦、張彥博、呂熙、台灣女星宋芸樺、英國女星愛瑪沃森（Emma Watson）、來自南非嘅騎師麥偉利，以及「新鮮出爐」嘅肥媽等，就連Emoji都可以撞樣，認真誇張！<br />\n<br />\n佢留言笑指：「講起撞樣呢單嘢其實我好攰，自從泰國捐精之後，我好似周街都會見到我自己，你明唔明自己會喺街度撞到自己嗰種驚法，我就嚟撞樣撞到上月球㗎喇我。究竟我仲要似幾多人？撞樣界巨頭，睇完個po我覺得自己有面盲症。」而同佢撞樣、現正懷孕嘅倪晨曦則笑稱：「現在有點擔心我的bb會不會和你撞樣。」"},{"pid":"257c40055b3ab4fbb4d53bffb76d923a5fc09663","tid":2234382,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:41:29.000Z","msg":"以下：<br />\n似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85d99b82c9a1e86af3441031112dfb8c40cad26","tid":2234382,"uid":71166,"like":11,"dislike":15,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4dN.8.pS1dO7vZzftX0yPg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NjA3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/2ff7db41-08a9-11eb-bffb-3fbbe21dd0e9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4dN.8.pS1dO7vZzftX0yPg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NjA3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F2ff7db41-08a9-11eb-bffb-3fbbe21dd0e9&h=eb659d